conflictsWith[0]:
sections[6]{title,body}:
  Problem Statement,Provide a concrete runnable reference project that demonstrates structured documentation in practice without friction.
  Target Users,Engineers PMs and AI agents need a compact sample of TOON-first development.
  Core Features,Create update search filter complete and delete tasks with local persistence plus priority due date tags and notes.
  Quality Rules,The project must keep markdown source files out of root paths and generate human-readable docs from TOON.
  Non-functional Requirements,Fast local startup clear starter workflows and deterministic doc outputs for auditability.
  Completion Criteria,Install dependencies run npm run dev and docs:check strict; generated docs are present and fresh.
